{"tid":2142381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DareDsetutor 藍扮黃騙手足錢 條友拍戲拍到癡Q左線","createTime":"2020-08-06T11:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T12:18:57.000Z","uid":365136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9dde92e578a39d3f950b86f288bca0f3dbfe75","tid":2142381,"uid":365136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"Hello,PAGE主耽誤閣下片刻。希望閣下會能為以下事項作廣傳，以免其他同學矇騙受害。DareDseTutor 負責人是男爵貓社前負責（因臭名遠播，自行繁殖名種貓且售賣病貓，其後改名。）名改木天貓cafe，繼續售賣病貓。而環境衛生惡劣，一心賣貓求暴利，漠視貓隻健康。更「聲稱」cafe，只有幫客戶買外賣，但曾在社交網站稱研究新菜式。其後開補習社（鬥勝工房），即是DareDseTutor前身。第一，DareDseTutor筆記、範文、功課以及模擬試卷分別向LIHKG 金娜娜、考評局以及出版社模擬試卷。第二，其DSE英文科Level 4 成積保證之一項條款為完成所有功課，而功課之多耗費時間。第三，而功課文章批改走馬看花，不見認真之處。第四，其發音極其惡劣。第五，退款期限於7月30日，但其客服聯絡不果，懷疑刻意斷絕聯絡，逃避學生之退款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOoB3h9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOoB3h9.png&h=c3ab1798&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6g179Ya.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6g179Ya.png&h=d03cb5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jxjqcbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxjqcbw.png&h=4843b9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7mzPYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7mzPYb.png&h=03f32a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12Vdk4S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12Vdk4S.png&h=cbe7c14a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETbgiRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETbgiRy.png&h=5bc5c560&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1aAzpU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1aAzpU.png&h=672b9728&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUmj04U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUmj04U.png&h=05cf8ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><img s